            <div type="a">
                <column>02</column>
                <head>Is Benjamin F. Meyers a Free Trader?</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <trailer/>
                <names>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Meyers</ln>
                        <fn>Benjamin</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Cessna</ln>
                        <fn>John</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>The paper asserts that Benjamin Meyers, Congressman-elect from the district
                    including Franklin, is a free trade advocate. John Cessna, who is challenging
                    Meyers's narrow victory, is a staunch protectionist.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>

