            <div type="a">
                <column>01</column>
                <head>Dr. Willetts' Lecture</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The paper declares Dr. Willetts' lecture a success despite small crowds. He
                    spoke in "Sunshine, or the Search of a Happy Life." The talk centered on the
                    importance of optimism, happiness, and geniality that he termed the "sunshine of
                    the heart." The paper attributes the small attendance from the lingering effects
                    of Olive Logan's "inspipid twaddle" at the most recent high-profile lecture.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>

